channel.title: Compiler says ... 100 errors? Do I need a new compiler?
channel.description: It says compiling finished then it says 100 errors And my compiler never updates server?

item.title: Compiler says ... 100 errors? Do I need a new compiler?
item.dc:creator: @tonypker13 tonypker13
item.description:
@tonypker13 wrote:

[quote=“bencorbett, post:4, topic:248183”]No - Your compiler is fine.
100 errors usually means you’ve forgotten a bracket or added one too many brackets in your source code, so go back and check over the parts you changed before you tried to compile, making sure your brackets match up.[/quote]
Usually is that key word.
If you completely fuck up your method. That’s another way
